      • replace

        public abstract FractionScheduler replace​(int containerComponentId,
                                          Fraction fraction)
        Replaces a specified Fraction instance in the container identified by the given containerComponentId.

        If the specified Fraction already exists in the container, this method will replace it. Otherwise, this method is equivalent to the add operation.

        Parameters:
        containerComponentId - Identifies the container where the Fraction instance will be replaced.
        fraction - Indicates the Fraction instance to replace.
        Returns:
        Returns the FractionScheduler instance used to perform the Fraction transaction.

        4
